---

## Why convert text into numbers?

Machine learning algorithms only understand numerical values.

---

## Why split dataset?

To test real performance of model.

---

## Why use Naive Bayes in spam filtering?

Works efficiently for text classification.

---

## What is normalization?

Scaling values into smaller range for balanced learning.
